<br>
What is everyones &quot;go to&quot; fly on the norfork and how do you fish it?<br>
<br>
Thanks Guys<br>
<br>
Brian <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F9FBFD><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bflyfishingarkansasandmissouri.showUserPublicProfile?gid=flyfishar>FlyFishAR</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>ezOP</span><br>  Posts: 433<br> <font color=#000000>(8/13/03 11:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fflyfishingarkansasandmissourifrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.flyfishingarkansas.com/Photo%20Gallery/tn_j.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Chuck's Emerger</span><hr size=1> Brian:<br>
